===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}}, from {{etyl|fro|en}}, from {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|distantia||distance, remoteneness, difference|lang=la}}, from {{term/t|la|distāns}}, present participle of {{term/t|la|distō||I stand apart, I am separate, distant, or different}}, from {{term|di-|lang=la}}, {{term|dis-||apart|lang=la}} + {{term/t|la|stō||I stand}}.

